Method Details [hide private]

__test_cases_from_cfg(self, cases, test, cluster_name='c1')

source code 

Tests all cases by loading a cluster template from the test config. This method will write a custom test config for each case using its settings.

__test_cases_from_cluster(self, cases, test)

source code 

Tests all cases by manually loading a cluster template using the Cluster class. All settings for a case are passed in as constructor keywords. Avoids the config module by using the Cluster object directly to create a test case.
